      <title>hexo+nexT 开发学习</title>
      <link href="/2020/02/12/Hexo+next%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/"/>
      <url>/2020/02/12/Hexo+next%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>用于 hexo + nexT 开发测试</p><a id="more"></a><h1 id="1-评论"><a href="#1-评论" class="headerlink" title="1.评论"></a>1.评论</h1><h2 id="1-添加评论"><a href="#1-添加评论" class="headerlink" title="1. 添加评论"></a>1. 添加评论</h2><p>注册LeanCloud账号，新建应用，获取AppID和AppKey，在主题配置文件中配置”valine“，即可实现评论功能，数据上传至LeanCloud新建应用“存储”中，可在后台管理中进行数据管理。</p><h2 id="2-删除评论"><a href="#2-删除评论" class="headerlink" title="2.删除评论"></a>2.删除评论</h2><p>在LeanCloud新建应用“存储”中，可在后台管理中进行数据管理，进行评论的删除。</p><p>也可进行其他配置。</p><p>也可进行其他配置。</p><h1 id="2-Debugger"><a href="#2-Debugger" class="headerlink" title="2.Debugger"></a>2.Debugger</h1><h2 id="1-symbols-count-time"><a href="#1-symbols-count-time" class="headerlink" title="1.symbols_count_time:"></a>1.symbols_count_time:</h2><p>256行</p><p>在站点配置文件中添加</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#wordcount</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">symbols_count_time:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">symbols:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">time:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">total_symbols:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">total_time:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">exclude_codeblock:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在主题配置文件中</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">symbols_count_time:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">separated_meta:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">item_text_post:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">item_text_total:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">awl:</span> <span class="number">4</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">wpm:</span> <span class="number">275</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="2-related-posts"><a href="#2-related-posts" class="headerlink" title="2.related_posts:"></a>2.related_posts:</h2><p>290行</p><p>在站点根目录中执行以下命令安装依赖：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-related-popular-posts --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在主题配置文件中开启相关文章推荐功能：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">themes\next_config.ymlrelated_posts:  enable: true  title: # custom header, leave empty to use the default one  display_in_home: false  params:    maxCount: 5</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>此时会在每篇文章结尾根据标签相关性和内容相关性来推荐相关文章。</p><p>&lt;&gt;</p><h2 id="3-post-edit"><a href="#3-post-edit" class="headerlink" title="3.post_edit:"></a>3.post_edit:</h2><p>303行</p><p>在主题配置文件下，如下配置</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">post_edit:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">url:</span> <span class="string">https://github.com/BobBoss/BobBoss.github.io/tree/master/2020/02/12</span> <span class="comment"># Link for view source</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="4-local-search"><a href="#4-local-search" class="headerlink" title="4.local_search:"></a>4.local_search:</h2><p>755行</p><p>现在站点目录下执行</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-search --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后在站点_config.yml文件中添加</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 搜索</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">search:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">path:</span> <span class="string">search.xml</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">field:</span> <span class="string">post</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">format:</span> <span class="string">html</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">limit:</span> <span class="number">10000</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="5-动画"><a href="#5-动画" class="headerlink" title="5.动画"></a>5.动画</h2><p>[]: <a href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-generator-searchdb" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-generator-searchdb</a>    “动画插件安装”</p><p>6.自定义头部图片</p><p>在/root/sorce/ 建立“_data”文件夹，在其中建立“styles.styl”文件，添加</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.site-meta &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background-image: url(<span class="regexp">/images/</span>log-big.jpg);</span><br><span class="line">  @media(min-width: <span class="number">992</span>px)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background-image: url(<span class="regexp">/images/</span>log-small.jpg);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>log-big.jpg也可以是其他名字。<code>log-big.jpg</code>的大小为<code>992×112</code>，<code>log-small.jpg</code>的大小为<code>240×112</code>，大了只能显示部分，小了可以重复铺满。</p><h2 id="6-文章置顶"><a href="#6-文章置顶" class="headerlink" title="6.文章置顶"></a>6.文章置顶</h2><p>根据top数值排序，越大越往上</p><h2 id="7-中英文之间自动添加空格"><a href="#7-中英文之间自动添加空格" class="headerlink" title="7.中英文之间自动添加空格"></a>7.中英文之间自动添加空格</h2><p>该功能由 <a href="https://github.com/vinta/pangu.js" target="_blank" rel="noopener">pangu</a> 提供，在根目录下执行如下命令克隆插件到项目中：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git clone https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;theme-next&#x2F;theme-next-pangu.git themes&#x2F;next&#x2F;source&#x2F;lib&#x2F;pangu</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在主题配置文件中设置 <code>pangu: true</code> 即可启用该动能。</p><h2 id="8-加入图片"><a href="#8-加入图片" class="headerlink" title="8.加入图片"></a>8.加入图片</h2><p>先下载建立资源文件夹的依赖：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>根目录下的_config.yml文件中post_asset_folder: false设置为true，以此打开文章资源文件夹功能；</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">当资源文件管理功能打开后，Hexo将会在你每一次通过 hexo new [layout] &lt;title&gt; 命令创建新文章时自动创建一个文件夹。这个资源文件夹将会有与这个 markdown 文件一样的名字。将所有与你的文章有关的资源放在这个关联文件夹中之后，你可以通过相对路径来引用它们，这样你就得到了一个更简单而且方便得多的工作流。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">正确的引用图片方式是使用下列的标签插件而不是 markdown ：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#123;%asset_img example.jpg This is an example image %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果是后来才打开此功能的，可以自己新建一个与md同名的文件夹，把图片放进去，然后按照文档所给的格式引用图片即可。</p><h2 id="9-文章结束标语"><a href="#9-文章结束标语" class="headerlink" title="9.文章结束标语"></a>9.文章结束标语</h2><p>参考3</p><h2 id="10-图片灯箱"><a href="#10-图片灯箱" class="headerlink" title="10.图片灯箱"></a>10.图片灯箱</h2><p>在根目录下执行以下命令安装相关依赖：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git clone https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;theme-next&#x2F;theme-next-fancybox3 themes&#x2F;next&#x2F;source&#x2F;lib&#x2F;fancybox</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在主题配置文件中设置 <code>fancybox: true</code>：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">themes\next_config.ymlfancybox: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>刷新浏览器即可生效。</p><h1 id="3-插件"><a href="#3-插件" class="headerlink" title="3.插件"></a>3.插件</h1><p>每次新建blog文件夹，在”hexo init”后，要下载</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>才能“hexo d”部署。</p><h1 id="4-文章写作"><a href="#4-文章写作" class="headerlink" title="4.文章写作"></a>4.文章写作</h1><h2 id="参考文章"><a href="#参考文章" class="headerlink" title="参考文章"></a>参考文章</h2><p><a href="https://www.lizenghai.com/archives/45250.html#15 " target="_blank" rel="noopener">1. 快速搭建博客教程</p><p><a href=" https://theme-next.org/docs/third-party-services/statistics-and-analytics#LeanCloud-China" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2. statistics-and-analytics</p><p><a href="https://asdfv1929.github.io/2018/01/28/add-the-end/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">3. 文章结语</p><p><a href="http://yearito.cn/posts/hexo-advanced-settings.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">4. 相关文章推荐</p>]]></content>
      
      
